OL,5, Charities are urging people to follow  
OL,6, Michael Sheen's lead and donate        
OL,7, unwanted items following huge losses   
OL,8, during the Covid lockdown.             
OL,10,FBritish Heart Foundation (BHF) Cymru   
OL,11,Fsaid it lost about #50m in the first   
OL,12,Fyear of Covid due to shop closures.    
OL,14,FOther charities echoed this loss and   
OL,15,Furged people to make donations, like   
OL,16,Fthe suits from Michael Sheen's parents.
OL,18,FAdam Fletcher, head of BHF Cymru, said 
OL,19,FCovid had been "devastating" for       
OL,20,Fcharities who rely on retail income.   
